{"tid":19140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【禽獸不如】2巴士司機輪流性侵15次 智障女懷孕要墮胎","createTime":"2016-12-02T16:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T09:28:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e14563d0a507eb26fe50cd8fc434f0a7bbf179fb","tid":19140,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161202/large/1480641006_b607.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161202%2Flarge%2F1480641006_b607.jpg&h=50284dcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">文字</span><br />\n台灣驚揭駭人性侵案。台北大都會客運一名巴士司機，見經常搭車的一名智障女乘客，在多次聊天後竟誘騙女方到家中性侵。令人髮指的是，司機竟向<br />\n<br />\n一同事透露向性侵智障女，該同事竟將巴士開到總站，在車上性侵對方十多次。直到智障女向另一名正義司機透露遭遇，正義司機才向女子母親揭露此事。母親報警後竟發現女兒已懷孕，只好帶女兒人工流產。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查，涉嫌性侵的55歲林恆遠及49歲司光宇任職巴士司機超過10年。受害女乘客年約20歲，外表清秀，與母親相依為命，每天巴士到市區工作，因而認識許多司機並利通訊軟件成為好友。<br />\n今年7月中，林男打電話邀受害人吃飯，女方應邀前往，卻被載回林家性侵，事後林男向司男炫耀。司男8月初接載受害人後，趁車上無其他乘客，竟開車回公司總站，直接關上車門窗對女方施暴。<br />\n警方指，受害人事後不敢向母親傾訴，直到十月，一名已離職的巴士司機與受害人用手機聊天時，她才透露事件。正義司機主動告知女子母親，母親即時報警，帶女兒到醫院檢查時，竟發現女兒已懷孕2個月，遂將胎兒人工流產。<br />\n警傳喚兩男，林男否認犯案，司男則坦承發生性關係10多次。警方統計受害人遭性侵約15次，訊後將兩人依妨害性自主罪嫌函送法辦。<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》  <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20161202/55993144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20161202%2F55993144&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=c2fc6d96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20161202%2F55993144&h=f5af8439\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20161202/55993144</a>"},{"pid":"0000f44b02dfc65471180209e3db3a28dd7aeb56","tid":19140,"uid":13307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 禽獸"},{"pid":"3e0f1b35787c4f9e689a7b1fb6017d3e3f85b540","tid":19140,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:07:37.000Z","msg":"巴士佬都係賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c93e6728f0cc294a9fa8239a004068b7e0c1713","tid":19140,"uid":5384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n賤畜<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac9c891ee6a971db4ccabab94929f7ac965d309","tid":19140,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:01:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d46d9188d0f0ee8476fdee51b0fc6ef7ba7b00b","tid":19140,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:03:03.000Z","msg":"台灣咁多女唔搞，搞智障女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be553e4aab7ac5bc5d199a0603df3beac78c8bb5","tid":19140,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T03:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161202/large/1480641006_b607.jpg\" data-thumbnail-